      <div class="ttl"><h3>Search bar inside the facet dropdown — “and the same everywhere”</h3>
        <div class="tags"><span class="pill done">✓ Done</span><span class="pill s-part">🟡 partial</span><span class="pill p1">P1</span><span class="pill eff">S</span></div>
      </div>
