      <div class="ttl"><h3>“Add to doc”: a diagram snapshot from Visualize into a document</h3>
        <div class="tags"><span class="pill done">✓ Done</span><span class="pill s-new">🔴 missing</span><span class="pill p1">P1</span><span class="pill eff">L</span></div>
      </div>
